    "Title": "Reclusive Bounty: ~mission(TargetName) | Extreme Risk",
    "Description": "--------------------------------------------------------\n-------------- BOUNTY CONTRACT ---------------\n--------------------------------------------------------\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nPROCESSING & DISTRIBUTION\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild has authorized an official bounty.\n\nNAME: ~mission(TargetName) \nRISK ASSESSMENT: Extreme\nLAST KNOWN LOCATION:  ~mission(Location|Address)\nKNOWN AFFILIATIONS: Unknown\nNOTES: This particular target has proven very difficult to capture. They tend to remain hidden unless there is a big enough threat to demand their attention. That's why you and your most trusted support fleet will need to take out enough of their underlings to force them to confront you. Just stay put, take out any hostiles that show up, and the target will eventually arrive in their capital ship.\n\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nIn Pursuit of Justice\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild is a security service sanctioned by the Mercenary Guild and authorized to operate in both the UEE and beyond in accordance with Xenotrade Authority Acts.",
